text:
you can also try the tag approach? If you're wanting specialization on the value.
```julia&gt; abstract type Vals end; 
struct A&lt;:Vals end; 
struct B&lt;:Vals end; 
struct C&lt;:Vals end; 
struct D&lt;:Vals end;

julia&gt; mutable struct MyStruct{T&lt;:Vals}
       h::T
       end```

